Starscream could here mumbles coming from inside the cave, but 
nothing that he could understand. He began to shout again.

"Predacons! It is I, great Decpticon warrior Starscream! I have taken 
a Beast Mode and now wish to join you. I have no craving for power," 
and tahn in a softer voice so no one could here he said "yet.
(shouting)All I care about is the destruction of the Maximals! Now 
let me in!!!!"
